title: Dire Straits Live On Every Street Basel Switzerland 1992 XviD Pr
description: Never before released until now Pre-broadcast version of Dire Straits live in Basel Switzerland 1992 On Every Street Tour. This is sourced from an original pre-broadcast copy of the concert before retransmission by TV and includes pre-concert footage. Video is VHS with no channel logo, Sound is HiFi stereo with pre-broadcast uncompressed sound. Duration 2h 16m 49s
